Fresh Pi session: CODE REVIEW.

Inputs:
- Jira ticket: {{run.dir}}/ticket.json
- Design doc: {{run.dir}}/design/design.md
- Manual test report: {{run.dir}}/manual-review/report-{{run.round}}.md

Rules:
- Do not edit source code.
- Review diff against base branch.
- Produce actionable issues only.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/code-review/report-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/code-review/status-{{run.round}}.json
- If failing: {{run.dir}}/code-review/issues-{{run.round}}.json
